name: Blue Felt Flat
description: This navy blue and light pink flower is made from felt and tulle, with a cute lil' bird in the middle. This flower drapes flat on a crocheted or satin headband, and is about 4" wide. It has an alligator clip on the back, making it easy to clip onto a headband, or clothing.

name: Purple Petals
description: This purple felt flower is made of felt, fabric and a fabric button. It is about 3 1/2" wide, and has an alligator clip on the back. It would look great as an accessory on a purse or on a pretty blouse. And of course, on a headband or in your hair!
